# Unified Sales Document System

Replace the existing invoice-only approach with a unified system supporting **Quotations**, **Delivery Notes**, and **Invoices** from a single builder page. Each line item supports per-item **discount %**, **discount value**, and **tax %**. Documents can be converted between types (Quotation → Delivery Note → Invoice) with full data carry-forward.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database migration**: The DB version will bump from V2 → V3. Existing `invoices` and `invoice_items` data will be migrated into the new `sales_documents` and `sales_document_items` tables as Invoice-type documents. The old tables are kept as-is (SQLite doesn't drop tables during migration).

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **File renames**: The existing [invoice_bloc.dart](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/presentation/bloc/invoice_bloc.dart), [invoice_event.dart](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/presentation/bloc/invoice_event.dart), [invoice_state.dart](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/presentation/bloc/invoice_state.dart), [invoice_builder_page.dart](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/presentation/pages/invoice_builder_page.dart), and [invoice_list_page.dart](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/presentation/pages/invoice_list_page.dart) will be replaced with new `sales_doc_*` equivalents. The old files will be deleted.

