## Proposed Changes

### Constants & Enums

#### [MODIFY] [app_constants.dart](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/core/constants/app_constants.dart)

- Add `DocType` enum: `quotation`, `deliveryNote`, `invoice`
- Add `DocStatus` enum: `draft`, `confirmed`, `cancelled`
- Bump `dbVersion` from `2` → `3`

---

### Domain Entities

#### [MODIFY] [invoice.dart → sales_document.dart](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/domain/entities/invoice.dart)

Rename file to `sales_document.dart`. Replace [Invoice](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/domain/entities/invoice.dart#7-89) entity with `SalesDocument`:

New/changed fields:
- `docType` (DocType) — quotation, deliveryNote, or invoice
- `docNumber` (String) — e.g. QUO-00001, DN-00001, INV-00001
- `discountAmount` (double) — total discount across all items
- `sourceDocId` (int?) — foreign key to the document this was converted from
- `sourceDocNumber` (String?) — display reference to the original doc
- `deliveryDate` (DateTime?) — for delivery notes
- `paymentStatus` (String?) — for invoices: paid/unpaid/partial

Replace [InvoiceItem](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/domain/entities/invoice.dart#91-162) with `SalesDocItem`:
- `discountPercent` (double) — per-item discount %
- `discountAmount` (double) — computed per-item discount value  
- `taxPercent` (double) — per-item tax %
- `taxAmount` (double) — computed per-item tax value
- `lineTotal` — now = [(unitPrice × qty) - discountAmount + taxAmount](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/data/models/invoice_model.dart#54-66)

New [recalculate()](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/domain/entities/invoice.dart#36-42) logic: aggregate subtotal, total discount, total tax, grand total from item-level calculations.

