### Data Layer — Datasource

#### [MODIFY] [sales_local_datasource.dart](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/data/datasources/sales_local_datasource.dart)

- Add `getNextDocNumber(DocType)` — generates `QUO-XXXXX`, `DN-XXXXX`, or `INV-XXXXX`
- Add `saveDocument(SalesDocument)` — insert or update a draft
- Add `getDocuments({DocType? filter})` — list all docs with optional type filter
- Add `getDocumentById(int id)` — fetch full doc with items + customer
- Refactor `confirmDocument(SalesDocument)` — type-aware: only deducts stock for delivery notes and invoices; quotations don't affect stock
- Add `convertDocument(int sourceId, DocType targetType)` — creates a new document from an existing one, linking via `source_doc_id`
- Update BI queries ([getRevenueToday](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/data/datasources/sales_local_datasource.dart#275-287), [getTopSellingItems](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/data/repositories/sales_repository_impl.dart#51-54)) to query `sales_documents`/`sales_document_items` instead of old tables

