#### [NEW] [sales_doc_builder_page.dart](file:///Users/fitpass-growth/Documents/stock_pilot/lib/features/sales/presentation/pages/sales_doc_builder_page.dart)

Single page for creating/editing any document type:
- **Document type selector** — SegmentedButton: Quotation / Delivery Note / Invoice
- **Customer section** — searchable dropdown (same customer picker)
- **Product entry table** — columns: Product (searchable), Qty, Unit Price, Discount %, Tax %, Line Total, Actions
- **Totals section** — Subtotal, Total Discount, Total Tax, Grand Total (auto-calculated)
- **Dynamic UI** — when Delivery Note is selected, price/tax columns can be collapsed; when Quotation, confirm button says "Save Quotation" (no stock impact)
- **Delivery date picker** — visible only for Delivery Notes
- **Notes field**
- **Actions** — Save Draft, Confirm

